title: 282: Missing Prospect for Super Bowl contenders, Evaluating the DB class
itunes:title: 282: Missing Prospect for Super Bowl contenders, Evaluating the DB class
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks each pick prospects that would fill the biggest need on a few of the Super Bowl contending franchises (7:00). The guys then dive into the 2018 defensive back class before they take you inside a prospect's visit with a team (16:02). Jacksonville wide receiver Dede Westbrook joins DJ and Bucky towards the end of the show to talk about Blake Bortles as well as a few of his fellow young Jaguar stars (36:42).
